This PR merges `extract_from_program` and `extract_from_multiple_program` since they are basically the same so we should not maintain two functions. The major motivation is that there are some bugs/outdated code in `extract_from_multiple_program` that result in crash.

A unit test is added as well to cover `extract_from_multiple_program`.

@eqy could you review this PR? Thanks.

Previously we fall back to float computation when the scale is not power of 2. This PR uses fixed point multiplications instead. 
See discussion in https://discuss.tvm.ai/t/quantization-float-multiplication-after-conv/4135/3

